{"tid":592322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"霍金二妻被爆洩「床事」女上狂un宣示主權","createTime":"2018-03-14T06:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T06:28:32.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7123c57b26ef118b294ccc75e0bbd454b2a7a6","tid":592322,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"英國物理學家霍金（ Stephen Hawking）逝世，有二段婚姻，而第二任妻子傳曾虐待他！<br />\n霍金的第二任妻子，原本也是霍金的護士伊蓮．梅森（ Elaine Mason），2004年、英國《每日鏡報》曾訪問一名前看護，她表示霍金的妻子伊蓮會虐待霍金，「記得有天我看見霍金頸項有一道傷痕。伊蓮一定很粗暴為他剃鬚。那不是普通剃傷，傷口達7.6釐米。」<br />\n<br />\n看護還說：「我們全部人見過霍金受虐待。另一次她把他的手腕重重擲到輪椅上，令他腕骨折斷。另一名看護看見了，就吃了不少苦頭。伊蓮常常擔心別人威脅她的地位。」甚至，看護驚爆伊蓮甚至會讓看護們看她和霍金做愛，「她會全身赤裸坐在他身上。那時，我還以為自己不對，騷擾他們夫妻親熱。後來發現原來很多人都看過。這是為了展示他們還有性關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180314/640_b11c14f330f17d0ef67ce05dec7471ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180314%2F640_b11c14f330f17d0ef67ce05dec7471ce.jpg&h=cbc080d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4456dd149515b61cd05290c372065744d3c6bb10","tid":592322,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/142641_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F142641_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d12e8dce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aac5f51e26d9450b68e7da5b9b26d1f736cf9936","tid":592322,"uid":136770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「記得有天我看見霍金頸項有一道傷痕。伊蓮一定很粗暴為他剃鬚。那不是普通剃傷，傷口達7.6釐米。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一代偉人竟然比人虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj